Project title: “The role of the microbiota on locomotion and social behaviour of the honey bee"

Project description: The project is using the coordinate based trancking data from DLC software. The codes aims to
1. clean the data from frames that are not needed and the filtering the outliers, 
2. to make locomotion analysis such as velocity, total distance traveled, velecoity spread, 
3. to make social interaction analysissuch as interindividual distance, following behaviour, following etc.

